{"tid":1546984,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"義務心理諮詢與情緒支援","createTime":"2019-09-06T13:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:55:50.000Z","uid":89184,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"205806ea67b7dcd7d0197b37456ce2185553128b","tid":1546984,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:42:04.000Z","msg":"唔少朋友近月都經歷過唔同程度嘅壓力，可能會出現一啲情緒困擾或心理反應。<br />\n<br />\n大家未必相信現有嘅求助途徑，或者對自己嘅情況都唔太了解，又未必有經濟能力睇私家醫生/心理學家（尤其年輕學生）。依家有多一個途徑畀大家考慮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8PN3vOj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8PN3vOj.jpg&h=173615a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，之前已經開左post，如下：<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油心理治療義診（絕對保密，不問有冇發夢，小限額免費心理支援，學生優先）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536387</a><br />\n<br />\n希望能為大家出一分綿力，香港人加油!!"},{"pid":"1da7b3edf4a0ef3d7e00772efebc882c0661c110","tid":1546984,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:42:17.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1545337/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a39608b3b1babbd7aeb5327f86eef4ac11d59149","tid":1546984,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:42:33.000Z","msg":"請幫推"},{"pid":"ad3642b131df95f4c7473515ec8fc2aa2724b859","tid":1546984,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T13:42:43.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"eb488016b75db40595206ed78f4612e5342314e0","tid":1546984,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci